[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":223},["ShallowReactive",2],{"/2025/06/28-1/markdown-huanhang":3,"surround-/2025/06/28-1/markdown-huanhang":212},{"id":4,"title":5,"body":6,"categories":188,"date":190,"description":191,"draft":192,"extension":193,"image":194,"meta":195,"navigation":196,"path":197,"readingTime":198,"recommend":203,"references":203,"seo":204,"stem":205,"tags":206,"type":203,"updated":210,"__hash__":211},"content/posts/2025/06/28-1/markdown-huanhang.md","Markdown 换行语法",{"type":7,"value":8,"toc":181},"minimark",[9,22,26,34,90,94,106,114,125],[10,11,12],"blockquote",{},[13,14,15,16],"p",{},"原文链接: ",[17,18,19],"a",{"href":19,"rel":20},"https://markdown.com.cn/basic-syntax/line-breaks.html",[21],"nofollow",[23,24,5],"h2",{"id":25},"markdown-换行语法",[13,27,28,29,33],{},"在一行的末尾添加两个或多个空格，然后按回车键,即可创建一个换行(",[30,31,32],"code",{},"\u003Cbr>",")。",[35,36,37,54],"table",{},[38,39,40],"thead",{},[41,42,43,48,51],"tr",{},[44,45,47],"th",{"align":46},"center","Markdown语法",[44,49,50],{"align":46},"HTML",[44,52,53],{"align":46},"预览效果",[55,56,57],"tbody",{},[41,58,59,72,82],{},[60,61,62,65,68,69],"td",{"align":46},[30,63,64],{},"This is the first line.  ",[66,67],"br",{},"  ",[30,70,71],{},"And this is the second line.",[60,73,74,77,79],{"align":46},[30,75,76],{},"\u003Cp>This is the first line.\u003Cbr>",[66,78],{},[30,80,81],{}," And this is the second line.\u003C/p>",[60,83,84],{"align":46},[13,85,86,87,89],{},"This is the first line.",[66,88],{}," And this is the second line.",[23,91,93],{"id":92},"换行line-break用法的最佳实践","换行（Line Break）用法的最佳实践",[13,95,96,97,100,101,103,104],{},"几乎每个 Markdown 应用程序都支持两个或多个空格进行换行，称为 ",[30,98,99],{},"结尾空格（trailing whitespace)"," 的方式，但这是有争议的，因为很难在编辑器中直接看到空格，并且很多人在每个句子后面都会有意或无意地添加两个空格。由于这个原因，你可能要使用除结尾空格以外的其它方式来换行。幸运的是，几乎每个 Markdown 应用程序都支持另一种换行方式：HTML 的 ",[30,102,32],{}," 标签。",[66,105],{},[13,107,108,109,111,112],{},"为了兼容性，请在行尾添加“结尾空格”或 HTML 的 ",[30,110,32],{}," 标签来实现换行。",[66,113],{},[13,115,116,117,120,121,124],{},"还有两种其他方式我并不推荐使用。CommonMark 和其它几种轻量级标记语言支持在行尾添加反斜杠 (",[30,118,119],{},"\\",") 的方式实现换行，但是并非所有 Markdown 应用程序都支持此种方式，因此从兼容性的角度来看，不推荐使用。并且至少有两种轻量级标记语言支持无须在行尾添加任何内容，只须键入回车键（",[30,122,123],{},"return","）即可实现换行。",[35,126,127,137],{},[38,128,129],{},[41,130,131,134],{},[44,132,133],{"align":46},"✅  Do this",[44,135,136],{"align":46},"❌  Don't do this",[55,138,139,161],{},[41,140,141,152],{},[60,142,143,146,148,149],{"align":46},[30,144,145],{},"First line with two spaces after.  ",[66,147],{}," ",[30,150,151],{},"And the next line.",[60,153,154,148,157,148,159],{"align":46},[30,155,156],{},"First line with a backslash after.\\",[66,158],{},[30,160,151],{},[41,162,163,172],{},[60,164,165,168,148,170],{"align":46},[30,166,167],{},"First line with the HTML tag after.\u003Cbr>",[66,169],{},[30,171,151],{},[60,173,174,177,148,179],{"align":46},[30,175,176],{},"First line with nothing after.",[66,178],{},[30,180,151],{},{"title":182,"searchDepth":183,"depth":183,"links":184},"",4,[185,187],{"id":25,"depth":186,"text":5},2,{"id":92,"depth":186,"text":93},[189],"技术分享","2025-06-28 22:45:50","Markdown 换行语法，如何创建换行以及最佳实践",false,"md","https://photo-kemiao.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/markdown-huanhang.webp-ys",{},true,"/2025/06/28-1/markdown-huanhang",{"text":199,"minutes":200,"time":201,"words":202},"2 min read",1.75,105000,350,null,{"title":5,"description":191},"posts/2025/06/28-1/markdown-huanhang",[207,208,209],"Markodwn","语法","换行","2025-06-28 23:21:50","LdFt7xMCNCf6SMMZauK9e77jH94q07PtdsVZzp_vfMo",[213,218],{"title":214,"path":215,"stem":216,"date":217,"type":203,"children":-1},"Markdown 段落语法","/2025/06/28/markdown-duanluo","posts/2025/06/28/markdown-duanluo","2025-02-13 14:04:50",{"title":219,"path":220,"stem":221,"date":222,"type":203,"children":-1},"Git 同步上游仓库的更新","/2025/04/04/git-tongbu","posts/2025/04/04/Git-tongbu","2025-04-04 20:13:15",1756211677329]